<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PayFlow - Soluciones de Pago en Línea</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%);
            color: #333;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* HEADER CON NAVEGACIÓN */
        header {
            background: rgba(15, 25, 50, 0.98);
            padding: 1.5em 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        header nav {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 2em;
        }

        .logo {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5em;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #0099ff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 1.5em;
            font-weight: 500;
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #0099ff);
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav a:hover::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* HERO SECTION */
        .hero {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 5em 2em;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
            animation: fadeInDown 1s ease;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5em;
            margin-bottom: 0.5em;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #fff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            animation: slideInUp 1s ease;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            margin-bottom: 2em;
            opacity: 0.95;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease;
        }

        .hero-subtext {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #00d4ff;
            margin-bottom: 2.5em;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1em 2.5em;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #0099ff);
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
            animation: bounceIn 1.5s ease;
            margin: 0 0.5em;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.6);
        }

        .cta-button.secondary {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #00d4ff;
            color: #00d4ff;
            box-shadow: none;
        }

        .cta-button.secondary:hover {
            background: #00d4ff;
            color: #0f1932;
        }

        /* CARACTERÍSTICAS */
        .features {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 4em auto;
            padding: 0 2em;
        }

        .features h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 3em;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2em;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2em;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            border-color: #00d4ff;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 1em;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature-card:hover .feature-icon {
            transform: scale(1.2) rotate(10deg);
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            color: #00d4ff;
            font-size: 1.4em;
            margin-bottom: 0.8em;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: #ddd;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* SERVICIOS CON TARJETAS */
        .servicios {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 4em auto;
            padding: 0 2em;
        }

        .servicios h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 3em;
        }

        .cards-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 2em;
        }

        .service-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2.5em;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .service-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s ease;
        }

        .service-card:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-15px);
            border-color: #0099ff;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .service-icon {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 1em;
        }

        .service-card h3 {
            color: #1e3c72;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-bottom: 1em;
        }

        .service-card p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 1.5em;
        }

        .price {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            color: #0099ff;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 1em;
        }

        .service-button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #0099ff);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.8em 1.8em;
            border-radius: 25px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .service-button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.4);
        }

        /* FORMULARIO DE CONTACTO */
        .contact-section {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 4em auto;
            padding: 3em 2em;
            border-radius: 20px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
        }

        .contact-section h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.2em;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 2em;
        }

        .contact-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 3em;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .contact-form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.2em;
        }

        .form-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .form-group label {
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 0.5em;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .form-group input,
        .form-group textarea {
            padding: 0.8em;
            border: 2px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        .form-group input::placeholder,
        .form-group textarea::placeholder {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        }

        .form-group input:focus,
        .form-group textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #00d4ff;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .form-group textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 120px;
        }

        .submit-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #0099ff);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 1em;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .submit-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .contact-info {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.5em;
        }

        .info-item {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 1.5em;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .info-item:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            border-color: #00d4ff;
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

        .info-icon {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-bottom: 0.5em;
        }

        .info-item h3 {
            color: #00d4ff;
            margin-bottom: 0.3em;
        }

        .info-item p {
            color: #ddd;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .form-message {
            padding: 1em;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: none;
            animation: slideDown 0.3s ease;
        }

        .form-message.success {
            background: #10b981;
            color: #fff;
            display: block;
        }

        .form-message.error {
            background: #ef4444;
            color: #fff;
            display: block;
        }

        @keyframes slideDown {
            from { transform: translateY(-20px); opacity: 0; }
            to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
        }

        /* CHAT EN VIVO */
        .chat-widget {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            z-index: 300;
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        .chat-button {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #0099ff);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50%;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.4);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        .chat-button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.6);
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.4); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 8px 35px rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.8); }
        }

        .chat-box {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 80px;
            right: 0;
            width: 380px;
            height: 500px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            display: none;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: slideUp 0.3s ease;
        }

        .chat-box.active {
            display: flex;
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from { transform: translateY(20px); opacity: 0; }
            to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
        }

        .chat-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72, #2a5298);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1.5em;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .chat-header h3 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .chat-close {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1.3em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .chat-close:hover {
            transform: scale(1.2);
        }

        .chat-messages {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding: 1.5em;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1em;
            background: #f9fafb;
        }

        .message {
            display: flex;
            animation: messageIn 0.3s ease;
        }

        @keyframes messageIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .message.user {
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        .message-content {
            max-width: 70%;
            padding: 0.8em 1em;
            border-radius: 10px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .message.bot .message-content {
            background: #e5e7eb;
            color: #333;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 10px 0;
        }

        .message.user .message-content {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #0099ff);
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 10px;
        }

        .chat-input-area {
            padding: 1em;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.5em;
        }

        .chat-input {
            flex: 1;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 0.7em 1em;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .chat-input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #0099ff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .chat-send {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #0099ff);
            border: none;
            color: #fff;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .chat-send:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        /* LICENCIA */
        .license-section {
            background: #fff;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 4em auto;
            padding: 3em 2em;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
        }

        .license-section h2 {
            color: #0099ff;
            margin-bottom: 1.5em;
            font-size: 2em;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #0099ff;
            padding-bottom: 0.5em;
        }

        .license-tabs {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1em;
            margin-bottom: 2em;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .license-tab {
            padding: 0.8em 1.5em;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            border-radius: 25px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #666;
        }

        .license-tab:hover {
            background: #0099ff;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .license-tab.active {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #0099ff);
            color: #fff;
        }

        .license-content {
            display: none;
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
        }

        .license-content.active {
            display: block;
        }

        .license-content h3 {
            color: #1e3c72;
            margin-bottom: 1em;
            margin-top: 1em;
        }

        .license-content p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 1em;
        }

        /* FOOTER */
        footer {
            background: rgba(15, 25, 50, 0.98);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 3em 2em;
            margin-top: 4em;
        }

        .footer-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 2em;
        }

        .footer-section h3 {
            color: #00d4ff;
            margin-bottom: 1em;
        }

        .footer-section a {
            color: #ddd;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.7em;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .footer-section a:hover {
            color: #00d4ff;
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1em;
            margin-top: 1em;
        }

        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #0099ff);
            border-radius: 50%;
            line-height: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .social-links a:hover {
            transform: scale(1.2) rotate(10deg);
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
            padding-top: 2em;
            text-align: center;
            color: #aaa;
        }

        /* ANIMACIONES */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes slideInUp {
            from { transform: translateY(30px); opacity: 0; }
            to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes bounceIn {
            0% { transform: scale(0.8); opacity: 0; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
        }

        /* RESPONSIVE */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2em; }
            .contact-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            nav a { margin: 0 0.8em; font-size: 0.85em; }
            .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .cards-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .chat-box { width: 100%; height: 400px; right: -100%; }
            .chat-widget.active .chat-box { right: 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- HEADER -->
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">💳 PayFlow</div>
            <div>
                <a href="#caracteristicas">Características</a>
                <a href="#servicios">Servicios</a>
                <a href="#contacto">Contacto</a>
                <a href="#licencia">Licencia</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Pagos en Línea Seguros y Rápidos</h1>
        <p>La plataforma de pago más confiable para tu negocio</p>
        <p class="hero-subtext">Procesa pagos internacionales, gestiona múltiples monedas y accede a analíticas avanzadas</p>
        <button class="cta-button" onclick="scrollToSection('contacto')">Comenzar Ahora</button>
        <button class="cta-button secondary" onclick="openChat()">💬 Chat en Vivo</button>
    </section>

    <!-- CARACTERÍSTICAS -->
    <section class="features" id="caracteristicas">
        <h2>🌟 Por Qué Elegir PayFlow</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🔐</div>
                <h3>Seguridad de Nivel Bancario</h3>
                <p>Encriptación de 256 bits, certificación PCI DSS y protección contra fraude en tiempo real.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
                <h3>Procesamiento Instantáneo</h3>
                <p>Confirmación de pagos en segundos con tecnología blockchain integrada.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🌍</div>
                <h3>Pagos Internacionales</h3>
                <p>Soporta 150+ monedas y opera en 195 países con conversión automática.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
                <h3>Analíticas Avanzadas</h3>
                <p>Dashboards en tiempo real con reportes detallados y gráficos personalizables.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">💰</div>
                <h3>Comisiones Competitivas</h3>
                <p>Desde 1.2% por transacción doméstica sin cargos ocultos.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🚀</div>
                <h3>API Poderosa</h3>
                <p>Integración simple con tu aplicación mediante nuestra API REST completa.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SERVICIOS -->
    <section class="servicios" id="servicios">
        <h2>💼 Nuestros Planes</h2>
        <div class="cards-container">
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">🎯</div>
                <h3>Starter</h3>
                <p>Perfecto para pequeños negocios y emprendedores que inician.</p>
                <div class="price">$0 de Setup</div>
                <ul style="color: #666; margin: 1em 0; list-style: none;">
                    <li>✓ Hasta 1,000 transacciones/mes</li>
                    <li>✓ Soporte por email</li>
                    <li>✓ Dashboard básico</li>
                    <li>✓ Comisión 2.9% + $0.30</li>
                </ul>
                <button class="service-button" onclick="selectPlan('Starter')">Seleccionar Plan</button>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">⭐</div>
                <h3>Professional</h3>
                <p>La opción ideal para empresas en crecimiento.</p>
                <div class="price">$99/mes</div>
                <ul style="color: #666; margin: 1em 0; list-style: none;">
                    <li>✓ Transacciones ilimitadas</li>
                    <li>✓ Soporte prioritario 24/7</li>
                    <li>✓ Reportes avanzados</li>
                    <li>✓ Comisión 1.9% + $0.25</li>
                </ul>
                <button class="service-button" onclick="selectPlan('Professional')">Seleccionar Plan</button>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">👑</div>
                <h3>Enterprise</h3>
